content: The Zhik 29er World Championships will be held in Gdynia, Poland on 26th July until 3rd August 2019 (Racing days 29th July-3rd Aug). Please be advised that as Gdynia is hosting the World Sailing Youth Championships which finish on the 20th July, there will be no access to the Venue until the 22nd July for trailers or competitors of the 29er Class Worlds.
